Day 28: Facilitate, Don’t Control!
🛠️ Facilitation creates flow, control creates friction!  
👉 Tip: Be a facilitator in every meeting. Guide conversations but let the team come to their own conclusions.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
-----

🧠 Poll: "How often do you act as a facilitator rather than a controller in meetings?"  
1. Always facilitate 🔄  
2. Most of the time 🤝  
3. Sometimes 🛠️  
4. I tend to control meetings 🛑
